videos.description: TCU QB Trevone Boykin finds WR Josh Doctson for a 9-yard TD to extend the Horned Frog's lead to 37-10. On that drive, Boykin breaks Andy Dalton's school record for total passing yards with 11,960.
videos.headline: Boykin makes TCU history
